er the age of 25, from the NBA and beyond.\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most interesting names\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Victor Wembanyama is... okay, he probably does not need an introduction.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Wembanyama\", \"score\": 0.9999841253316324, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Victor Wembanyama\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Wembanyama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Wembanyama\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an introduction\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wembanyama is the NBA's reigning Rookie of the Year following his status as arguably the most hyped draft prospect of all time or at the very least the most hyped international draft prospect of all time.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652738745170818e-61, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wembanyama\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"the Year\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"his status\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"arguably the